 1100 patients will be recruited by pharmacists.

 They will answer to a standardized questionnaire assessing their benzodiazepines or related drugs usage (phone contact).

 Pharmacists are recruited by all French Centers For Evaluation and Information on Pharmacodependence (CEIP).

